== 製作 ==
2011年5月1日，知名美國導演[[雷利·史考特|雷利·史考特]]買下了小說《-{[[別相信任何人|別相信任何人]]}-》的電影改編版權，並邀請{{link-en|羅文·約菲|Rowan Joffé}}編劇與執導。2012年2月，[[妮可·基嫚|妮可·基嫚]]加盟此片<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/nicole-kidman-in-talks-to-star-in-rowan-joffes-psychological-thriller-before-i-go-to-sleep |title=Nicole Kidman In Talks To Star In Rowan Joffe's Psychological Thriller 'Before I Go To Sleep' |access-date=2014-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113101757/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/nicole-kidman-in-talks-to-star-in-rowan-joffes-psychological-thriller-before-i-go-to-sleep |archive-date=2013-11-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，同年10月31日，[[馬克·史壯|馬克·史壯]]亦加入演員陣容<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://variety.com/2012/film/news/mark-strong-set-for-sleep-1118061486/ |title=Mark Strong set for 'Sleep' |accessdate=2014-04-26 |archive-date=2014-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726212509/http://variety.com/2012/film/news/mark-strong-set-for-sleep-1118061486/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年2月6日，[[柯林·佛斯|柯林·佛斯]]確定加入劇組<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/nicole-kidman-wants-colin-firth-391082 |title=Nicole Kidman Wants Colin Firth for S.J. Watson Thriller |accessdate=2014-04-26 |archive-date=2014-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227065814/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/nicole-kidman-wants-colin-firth-391082 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 反响 ==
美国首周末三天仅获得203万美元，分别创下了妮可·基德曼和科林·费斯两人主演影片职业生涯的最低记录。

此片的口碑比较差。根據[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]網站，新鮮度仅有37％<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/before_i_go_to_sleep/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-09-25 |archive-date=2014-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140929053646/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/before_i_go_to_sleep/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]網站則有42分（滿分100）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/before-i-go-to-sleep |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-09-25 |archive-date=2014-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010084602/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/before-i-go-to-sleep |dead-url=no }}</ref>；[[IMDb|IMDb]]平均為6.5分。英國《{{link-en|每日星報|Daily Star (United Kingdom)}}》的影評人Andy Lea則對[[妮可·基嫚|妮可·基嫚]]的表現給予正面評價<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.co.uk/movies/397176/Review-trailer-Before-I-Go-To-Sleep-starring-Nicole-Kidman-and-Colin-Firth |title=Review and trailer: Before I Go To Sleep (15) is a nail-biting tour de force |accessdate=2014-09-25 |archive-date=2014-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140925063902/http://www.dailystar.co.uk/movies/397176/Review-trailer-Before-I-Go-To-Sleep-starring-Nicole-Kidman-and-Colin-Firth |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

